ression and believed I&#039;d walk again. Every day she was pushing me she believed in me and it was hard for mum and me. I took my first steps 6 months after the attack. I know I would never have even got over my depression let alone walk again. I now walk unaided with a slight limp. This is just a fraction of what my mum has done for me and I can&#039;t ever express how grateful I am to her. She is football mad she supports her home town. Her beloved Coventry City. She never misses a game and we can&#039;t afford to go to alot of football matches alot so she listens on the radio. I&#039;d love to treat her and say thankyou for her help support and love she has for me. My mum deserves this so much and I know it would make her so happy if she won this. Thankyou for reading my story. Kelly Robson.   P. S  I put my details instead of my mums because I wasn&#039;t sure wether I was supposed to put hers or my contact information. Thank you. \";s:5:\"tandc\";s:1:\"1\";s:14:\"privacy-cookie\";s:1:\"1\";}','2020-11-03 04:26:38'),(550,55,'a:12:{s:12:\"cfdb7_status\";s:6:\"unread\";s:10:\"first-name\";s:7:\"Matthew\";s:9:\"last-name\";s:5:\"Rigby\";s:14:\"contact-number\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"email-add\";s:21:\"imlikematt@live.co.uk\";s:10:\"birth-date\";s:10:\"1992-05-25\";s:9:\"address-1\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"town-city\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"postcode\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"your-story\";s:1160:\"Matthew Rigby knows everything about football. We spend a lot of time travelling in Europe and every time we drive through a new town or city and pass a football stadium, he knows the name of the stadium and the team that plays there. Whenever he meets someone new, he asks where theyre from - and then tells them who their local football team is, who theyve recently signed, where they are in the league. Not just for English teams - Matt can do this for pretty much any town in Europe. Its great seeing peoples faces light up as theyre reminded of home and impressed by Matts incredible football knowledge. We