ed reading that son?&#039;as he smiled and winked.happy days from hibbitt,shoulder,withe i remember an away game.sub came on i said my best mate whos this? as he beat about 5 players.we looked at programme.peter beardsley.manu let him go he became my fav player then i remember watchin shearer scoring for southampton and then bein in tenerife watchin him come on as a sub for blackburn gettin the equaliser n sayin we hotta sign him..euro 96 shearer,gazza class..we gotta sign him..when my hero keegan signed him..i smiled thinking back to when keegan signed for us as a kid.Hairs standing up on back of my neck yet again looking forward\r\nIf only we&#039;d won the league.But as a toon fan i wouldnt change my childhood till now.listening to midweek games on the radio in bed.kids now dont get that feeling with all the technology...one game sticks in my head cause my dad woke me up when my younger brother was asleep and said get up you can watch sportsnight son.pillow on settee toast and cocoa il never forget that feeling.england v hungary trevor brooking sticking the ball in the stantion...keegan my hero playing a blinder.thanks dad for that memory.couldnt wait to do my paper round and get to school,copy the game in the schoolyard with our tennis ball..about 30 of us..happy days being a football fan!!\";s:5:\"tandc\";s:1:\"1\";s:14:\"privacy-cookie\";s:1:\"1\";}','2020-11-09 00:43:39'),(745,55,'a:12:{s:12:\"cfdb7_status\";s:6:\"unread\";s:10:\"first-name\";s:8:\"Ciprian \";s:9:\"last-name\";s:7:\"Corlan \";s:14:\"contact-number\";s:11:\"07858427504\";s:9:\"email-add\";s:27:\"corlanciprian1998@gmail.com\";s:10:\"birth-date\";s:10:\"1998-04-15\";s:9:\"address-1\";s:17:\"75 coltman street\";s:9:\"town-city\";s:5:\"Hull \";s:8:\"postcode\";s:7:\"HU32SJ \";s:10:\"your-story\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"tandc\";s:1:\"1\";s:14:\"privacy-cookie\";s:1:\"1\";}','2020-11-09 01:22:51'),(746,55,'a:12:{s:12:\"cfdb7_status\";s:6:\"unread\";s:10:\"first-name\";s:6:\"Philip\";s:9:\"last-name\";s:11:\"