ying to 4 or more different countries to get to Russia taking cheap flights to each just to get to the games and made many journeys back and forth to ensure he could keep his job while still attending every game.\r\n\r\nBut this is an understatement to how much John actually loves the game. He doesn&#039;t just follow England and Wigan and when there are no games he can make it too hear he will travel Europe to experience other leagues and game. Only last year he went to the partizan Derby as he just wanted to experience it as a football fan. \r\n\r\nI could write all day about John&#039;s love for football but I&#039;m not sure thet is actually enough words out there I don&#039;t even feel like I have done him enough justice but when your talking about the biggest overall football fan as a whole there really is no other like John Mez. \";s:5:\"tandc\";s:1:\"1\";s:14:\"privacy-cookie\";s:1:\"1\";}','2020-11-09 01:48:31'),(747,55,'a:12:{s:12:\"cfdb7_status\";s:6:\"unread\";s:10:\"first-name\";s:6:\"Daniel\";s:9:\"last-name\";s:5:\"Gooch\";s:14:\"contact-number\";s:11:\"07835480488\";s:9:\"email-add\";s:22:\"smoochyboi@outlook.com\";s:10:\"birth-date\";s:10:\"1982-03-31\";s:9:\"address-1\";s:18:\"11 Melbourne Road \";s:9:\"town-city\";s:7:\"Chatham\";s:8:\"postcode\";s:7:\"ME4 5PD\";s:10:\"your-story\";s:252:\"I pick my 10 year old daughter Maxey she went to Stamford bridge when she was a baba but since shes been really ill she hasnt managed to\r\nGo again and I think another trip to see her heroes would smile her up and make her feel better \";s:5:\"tandc\";s:1:\"1\";s:14:\"privacy-cookie\";s:1:\"1\";}','2020-11-09 02:31:44'),(748,55,'a:12:{s:12:\"cfdb7_status\";s:6:\"unread\";s:10:\"first-name\";s:8:\"Geoffrey\";s:9:\"last-name\";s:6:\"Redway\";s:14:\"contact-number\";s:11:\"01268471300\";s:9:\"email-add\";s:27:\"geoffrey.redway48@gmail.com\";s:10:\"birth-date\";s:10:\"1948-02-25\";s:9:\"address-1\";s:19:\"182 Church End Lane\";s:9:\"town-city\";s:8:\"WICKFORD\";s:8