ments he has in his life aside from his family, his loving wife two kids and grandkid. Carl has received honours for his charity work that him and his wife worked so hard on. Fundraising for a number of local causes. One of them being a local football team for the disabled, called skemmenaces (google it), carls the big bald one in the wheelchair.  This football team is more than just a football team it&#039;s  more than just football, it&#039;s giving these disabled people a new lease of life and breeds new confidence into them Put smiles on all their faces and gifts 15 new people to call friends. Carl and his amazing work is the centre of all of that. \r\n\r\nThen came 2020, Carl as suffered greatly during this pandemic losing a close friend Due to covid.  of course, the closure of his Beloved football team skemmenaces. Being one of the things in life that gives him more drive than anything, this is a devastating blow. He has worked so hard to set up the club againt all odds and now its looking like it might be the end if there isnt any imrovments soon.  Any way enough of the sob story he just isnt like that. He just cracks on. \r\n\r\nI recently donated 50 pounds, not to their causes but to them personally, telling them to go and enjoy themselves with the money, this Of course fell on deaf ears, as they wouldn&#039;t dream of it. So, this is another reason why i nominate carl to give him a prize for himself and his wife that he can&#039;t pass on to others. Another reason i want  Carl for this prize is I recently found out  that surprisingly even though he he football mad. He unfortunatley has never been to a live game at Anfield to watch his beloved Liverpool. As the disabled tickets are really hard to come by, although he would probably spend his money and time helping other people.\r\n If everyone was as selfless as carl and his wife the world would be magic. \r\n\r\nI think it will be fitting for him and his wife mirian to enjoy this together. Also GIVE IT TO 