demic.</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Use of information</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"start\":35} -->\n<ol start=\"35\"><li>Winning entrants first name and county may be published or made available to the public on request in order for the promoter to comply with regulatory obligations.</li><li>By entering into this promotion, each entrant agrees that any personal information provided in connection with the promotion may be held and used by the promoter (and/or its agents and suppliers) in order to administer the promotion and contact winners.</li><li>We will keep any personal information provided as part of an entry for a period of 3 months after the Promotional Period or in the case of winning entries, for 3 months after the prize has been spent.</li><li>Entrants and nominees have the right to exercise their rights (access, rectification, cancellation and opposition) by contacting dataprotection@gvcgroup.com.</li><li>We will use all personal data in accordance with <a><strong><u>Privacy and Cookie</u></strong></a><strong><u>.</u></strong></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>General</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true,\"start\":40} -->\n<ol start=\"40\"><li>Where the promoter suspects that any entrant or nominee is guilty of fraudulent activity, the promoter reserves the right to suspend or remove that individual from the promotion, and/or suspend that individuals account (where applicable) and/or suspend the promotion pending further investigation.</li><li>The promoter reserves the right to change, end or restrict your access to this promotion, if required for legal and/or regulatory reasons.&nbsp;</li><li>The promoter accepts no responsibility or liability for network, computer or software failures of any kind and has no responsibility for lost, delayed or misdirected entries.</li><li>The promoter shall not be liable for 